       "description": "Just like there is no charm equal to the tenderness of heart, the artistic appeal of this mesmerizing diamond ring by Senco is second to none. The artistic heart motif is beautifully designed with 0.19 carat diamonds in 18K gold, making it look more appealing. The design is elegant, just like the strong connection you share with the love of your life. Please note - The dimension of the actual product might vary.",
